<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lo">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ຈັດການລົດ</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+Lao:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/admin/dashboard">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Logo" style="height: 80px; margin-right: 15px;">
                ແຜງຄວບຄຸມແອດມິນ
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/manage-car">ຈັດການລົດ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/add-car">ເພີ່ມລົດໃໝ່</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/admin/manage-sell-requests">ຈັດການຄຳຂໍຂາຍ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" href="/">ໜ້າຫຼັກ</a>
                    <a class="nav-link text-danger" href="/admin/logout" onclick="return confirm('ທ່ານແນ່ໃຈບໍ່ທີ່ຈະອອກຈາກລະບົບ?');">ອອກຈາກລະບົບ</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="card bg-dark text-light">
            <div class="card-header bg-gold text-dark">
                <h2>ຈັດການລົດ</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <a href="/admin/add-car" class="btn btn-gold mb-3 w-100 w-md-auto">ເພີ່ມລົດໃໝ່</a>
                <table class="table table-striped bg-dark text-light">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>ຍີ່ຫໍ້</th>
                            <th>ລຸ້ນ</th>
                            <th>ປະເພດ</th>
                            <th>ປີ</th>
                            <th>ລາຄາ</th>
                            <th>ແຂວງ</th>
                            <th>ການກະທຳ</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <% if (cars.length === 0) { %>
                            <tr>
                                <td colspan="7" class="text-center">ບໍ່ມີລົດໃນລະບົບ.</td>
                            </tr>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <% cars.forEach(car => { %>
                                <tr>
                                    <td><%- car.brand %></td>
                                    <td><%- car.model %></td>
                                    <td><%- car.carType %></td>
                                    <td><%- car.year %></td>
                                    <td><%- car.price.toLocaleString() %> ກີບ</td>
                                    <td><%- car.province %></td>
                                    <td>
                                        <a href="/admin/edit-car/<%- car._id %>" class="btn btn-gold btn-sm">ແກ້ໄຂ</a>
                                        <form action="/admin/delete-car/<%- car._id %>" method="post" style="display: inline;">
                                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" onclick="return confirm('ທ່ານແນ່ໃຈບໍ່ທີ່ຈະລົບລົດນີ້?');">ລົບ</button>
                                        </form>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            <% }) %>
                        <% } %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer text-center bg-dark text-gold">
        <div class="container">
            <p>ທີ່ຢູ່: ນະຄອນຫຼວງວຽງຈັນ, ປະເທດລາວ</p>
            <p>ໂທ: +856 20 1234 5678</p>
            <p>ອີເມວ: contact@yourcarwebsite.com</p>
            <p>ຕິດຕາມພວກເຮົາ:
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/yourpage" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">Facebook</a> |
                <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@your.tiktok" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">TikTok</a>
            </p>
            <p>ດາວໂຫຼດແອັບ:
                <a href="https://play.google.com/store" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">Google Play</a> |
                <a href="https://www.apple.com/app-store/" target="_blank" class="text-gold mx-2">App Store</a>
            </p>
            <p>© 2025 Used Car Sales. ສະຫງວນລິຂະສິດ.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>